LOCUS       V5_tag                    14 aa            linear   UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  V5_tag — a 14-aa epitope tag (GKPIPNPLLGLDST) from the PIV5/SV5 P/V
            protein (UniProt P11208, residues 95–108), recognized by the
            high-affinity SV5-Pk1 monoclonal antibody for protein detection,
            purification, and imaging..
